locale.title: MonkeGodz
locale.description: 333 supply programmatically generated pixel gods NFT collection that will be released on NEAR. Each MonkeGodz holder will be able to cast a vote on the DeityDao, which will pave the way for the project's future!

signedOut.title: join the godz
signedOut.body:

Each MonkeGodz holder will gain voting rights in DeityDAO, paving the way for the project's future!
